NAME

DateTime::Locale::br_FR - Locale data examples for the Breton France (br-FR) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Breton France locale.

Date Formats

Full 

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Meurzh 5 Cʼhwevrer 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Gwener 22 Kerzu 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Sadorn 15 Gwengolo -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Cʼhwevrer 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Kerzu 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Gwengolo -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Cʼhwe. 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Kzu. 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Gwen. -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05/02/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/09/-10
